Name: WOMEN TRENDING COTTON  WHITE RIB TOP
Description: Name:WOMEN TRENDING COTTON  WHITE RIB TOP Top Fabric:Acrylic A women's rib tank top is a sleeveless garment designed to be worn as an outer layer or as an undershirt. It is made of ribbed fabric, which has a textured appearance due to its alternating raised and lowered rows. The tank top is typically form-fitting and stretches to fit the wearer's body.  The tank top may have a scoop neck, a V-neck, or a crew neck, depending on the style. It may also have a racerback design, which exposes the shoulders and upper back. The straps of the tank top are usually thin and can be adjustable or non-adjustable.  Ribbed tank tops can be made of a variety of materials, such as cotton, polyester, or a blend of both. They come in a range of colors and can be plain or have printed designs or logos. They are a popular choice for layering under jackets, blazers, or cardigans, or wearing alone during warmer weather. It typically consists of multiple layers of fabric that are sewn together, with different layers serving different purposes to provide comfort, absorbency, and leak protection. They are designed to be comfortable and practical, with enough room to carry essentials such as a wallet, phone, and keys, as well as small personal items like sunglasses, lip balm, or a small notebook.  Sling bags come in a variety of materials, such as leather, canvas, nylon, or synthetic materials, and are available in various colors and designs to suit different tastes and styles. They often feature multiple compartments, pockets, or zippers for easy organization and access to your belongings.  Sling bags are a versatile accessory that can be worn casually or dressed up for a more sophisticated look. They are ideal for anyone who wants to keep their hands free while running errands, traveling, or enjoying outdoor activities. With their practical design and stylish look, sling bags are a must-have addition to any wardrobe.

It typically consists of a chain, cord, or other material that is adorned with decorative elements such as gemstones, beads, pendants, or charms.  Necklaces come in a wide variety of styles and designs, ranging from simple and understated to bold and intricate. They can be made from a variety of materials, such as gold, silver, platinum, or other precious metals, as well as materials like leather, fabric, or beads.  Necklaces can be worn by both men and women and are a popular accessory that can complement any outfit. They can be worn on their own as a statement piece, or layered with other necklaces for a more unique and personalized look.  The length of a necklace can vary greatly, from short chokers that sit closely around the neck, to longer chains that hang down to the chest or even lower. The length of a necklace can affect its overall style and can be chosen based on personal preference or to complement the neckline of the garment being worn.  Overall, a necklace is a versatile and timeless piece of jewelry that can be worn for any occasion, whether it's a casual day out or a formal evening event. The Anarkali Suit is made up of a Long, Frock-Style. It varies in Length. Anarkali means "Pomegranate Blossom." Pomegranate is a delectable and well-known intriguing natural product that is widely grown in India. The bright color and fancy designs are prominent in the Anarkali suit. And with time bright and fancy designs became the signature Anarkali suit design. This makes them perfect for wedding ceremonies and parties. The Anarkali dress helps you stand out from the crowd. The various forms of regal Anarkali silhouette are also related to the Indian culture in many ways. The Indian Angarakha is very similar to Anarkali, and is closely associated to the Indian classical dance-form Kathak. In making the Anarkali suit, the dress is usually designed as an extended frock-style top combined with a bottom. While the top is typically flowy and can reach as far as the mid-knee, ankle, or floor length, it is, however, fitted around the bust from where large pleats flow downwards.
